long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
✅Navigate Your Tabs with Ease – Tab History Navigation Made Simple!

Tired of losing track of your browsing journey? This powerful Chrome extension lets you effortlessly switch back and forth through your tabs' navigation history, just like the back and forward buttons in your browser – but faster and more convenient!

✨Key Features:
Seamlessly navigate your tab history with quick keyboard shortcuts.
Avoid retracing your steps manually and keep your workflow smooth.
Perfect for researchers, multitaskers, and productivity enthusiasts.
Keyboard Shortcuts:

Windows:
    Alt + Z: Go back in your tab's history.
    Alt + Shift + Z: Move forward in your tab's history.
MacOS and Others:
    Ctrl + Z: Go back in your tab's history.
    Ctrl + Shift + Z: Move forward in your tab's history.

✅ Completely Free: No hidden charges or ads!
✅ Open Source: https://github.com/amrnth/TabHistoryNav
✅ Lightweight & Fast: Designed for seamless performance.

Download now and experience faster, smoother tab navigation that keeps you in control of your browsing journey.
